    "sections": {
      "A": "Opens on vi (Dm) with V/vi (A7), then a descending chromatic ii-V chain (F7, Bm7b5-Bbm6, Am7-Ab13, Gm7-C7) cadencing to I (F6); ends with iii-VI turnaround (Em7b5-A7)",
      "A1": "As A, cadencing to F6, then Fm7-Bb7 setting up the Eb bridge",
      "B": "I-ii-V-I in Eb (Ebmaj7/Fm7-Bb7/Eb6), then ii-V-I to C (Dm7-G7-C6), descending chromatic ii-Vs (Am7, F#m7b5-Fm6, Em7-Ebo7, Em7b5-A7) leading back home",
      "A2": "As A but with V/ii (D7) into Gm7-C7 to F, ending with plagal Bb7 and final I (F)"
    },
    "modulates": true,
    "modulation_note": "Bridge (B) opens in Eb major and passes through C major before descending chromatically back to the F/Dm home"
  },
